            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Returned Prisoners</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The editor writes about the return of Confederate prisoners and their
                    arrival in Richmond on Tuesday. The President and the Governor addressed them
                    there, after which some of the prisoners themselves spoke to the gathering.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
